caption:
You’re invited to Veg Club’s 2024-25 Welcome Event 🎉🌱

Join us on Friday, September 20th for free vegan pizza, drinks, snacks, games, and more! This is a great opportunity to make new friends at UofT and to meet fellow veggie lovers in the club. 

This fun and casual event is open to executive and Green Crew members only! If you haven’t signed up for Green Crew yet, please do so (link in bio) before RSVPing to this event.

When: Friday, September 20th from 6-9pm
Where: Hart House Room 3017
Who: all UofT Veg Club members 

🔗RSVP through the link in our bio by Thursday, September 19 to secure your spot (space permitting)

We look forward to meeting everyone next week!! 💚
